{{#section "subject"}}
Your Arcus Service Has Been Downgraded to Basic
{{/section}}

{{#section "plaintext-body"}}
Hi {{{_person.firstName}}},

You have successfully updated your service plan to Basic at {{{_place.name}}}.

The following changes will occur to your account:

* You will have to call and dispatch emergency responders in the event of a Security, Smoke, CO, or Panic alarm.
* If you have cellular backup, you will need to subscribe to the Backup Cellular add-on plan at {{{_redirectBaseUrl}}}/e_prodowngrade to keep the service.
* Clipped video storage will be 1 day instead of 30 days
* You will be unable to pin videos to your account
* And more....... ({{{_redirectBaseUrl}}}/e_prodowngrade)
{{/section}}

